Unlock the mysteries of “blockchain" and its connection to the "No Buy No Sell" prophecy with hosts Matthew Schanche and MacKenzie Drebit. Dive into blockchain within digital systems as US banks close, aiming for a full transition by November 2025. Learn unprecedented tracking capabilities of digital currency, smart cars and smart cities. Witness the transformative force of AI, now endorsed for military use. As predictions of an AI financial collapse loom, could the Universal Basic Income be on the horizon? Join Truth Matters on this journey into Bible Truths for our time.
